name: Large Crystal Cluster
category: Magical
footprint: 2x2
facing: no
shadow: yes
blocks_light: yes
height: 2
lights: [{"preset":"astral","x":1.0,"y":1.0,"color":"#bb88ff","intensity":0.7,"radius":7}]
placement: center
room_types: crystal-grotto, cave-living, elemental-earth-node, underdark-outpost, demiplane-laboratory
typical_count: few
clusters_with: crystal-shard, crystal-cluster, crystal-dust, crystal-heart, mineral-vein
notes: Large radial cluster of violet crystal shards; place as centerpiece or mineral vein feature. Shards radiate outward from the center.
