# === HITBOX ===
hitbox circle 1.0,1.0 0.75 z 0-2

# Outer luminous halo
circle 1.0,1.0 0.95 gradient-radial #6040b0 #0a0820 0.45
# Soft glow ring
circle 1.0,1.0 0.70 fill #7755cc 0.2
circle 1.0,1.0 0.55 fill #9977ee 0.22

# Rocky base mass
